data.description: Holly Springs charm. Your  two story brick home with 5.bedrooms (one down and 4 up )and 3 full baths. Features: circular drive in front with parking pad for motor home  with  electrical hook up. 20x20 one car garage and shop behind fence..    attic space for storage with stair access form bedroom closet. Formal Dining room off marble floored foyer, parlor, den with wood burning fireplace. Kitchen with rolling island that stays with house/ breakfast area.  Lots of closet space. 3/4 acre lot and large fenced back yard. Playhouse.  Backs up to pasture with horses you can see. Privacy. Very nice family home in town of Holly Springs . 30 minutes to Oxford and 30 minutes to Memphis. Access I-69 from Hwy. 7. New roof and fresh paint, insulated windows. In Historical District of Holly Springs
